On the honeypot VM as root:

sudo -i

ufw default deny incoming
ufw default allow outgoing

# allow Cowrie honeypot port for everyone
ufw allow 2222/tcp

# block real SSH port 22 for everyone initially
ufw deny 22/tcp

ufw enable
ufw status

exit

then: 

Any VM can SSH to 10.0.2.15:2222 (Cowrie).

Nobody can reach 10.0.2.15:22 (real SSH).

